      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Objective: Defend your beacon from 30 waves of invading zombies\n\nGame
    Mechanics:\n> Zombie waves spawn every 30 seconds\n> Each wave has more zombies\n>
    More zombies spawn in a lane each time the disrutor is destroyed\n\nGameplay:\n>
    Kill zombies to collect money\n> Spend money on items and stat upgrades in th
    shop\n> Collect power ups for temporary stat boosts\n\nControls:\n> WASD to move
    \n> Space to jump\n> Control to sprint \n> Left click to use / attack\n> Scroll
    Wheel / Num keys 1-5 to switch items\n> E to interact\n> Tab to open map\n> ESC
    to open menu

'
